channel.title: Comments on: Liz Taylor Moving On

item.title: By: Hamza Alduraidi
item.dc:creator: Hamza Alduraidi
item.description: Dear Liz.. It was a great pleasure working with you! I wish you the best of happiness and success in Denver and wherever you decide to be. I couldn't make it to today's event, but I will definitely see you before you leave and say my goodbyes.
item.content:encoded: Dear Liz.. It was a great pleasure working with you! I wish you the best of happiness and success in Denver and wherever you decide to be. I couldn’t make it to today’s event, but I will definitely see you before you leave and say my goodbyes.

item.title: By: Elizabeth Bayha
item.dc:creator: Elizabeth Bayha
item.description: Aw, Liz! 530 just won't be as bright and bubbly without you here! You will be missed!
